Class CoreData

  • java.lang.Object
    • core.comp3111.CoreData
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class CoreData
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Data storage class for the application. Primary attributes are a 2D matrix of DataTable objects, Hashtable of Charts and a singular instance of CoreData.
    Author:
    michaelfrost
